data.description: Gorgeous townhome spanning over 1600 square feet in desirable Lake Ridge subdivision! This 3 level townhome boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths & 2 half baths, 2 car garage & 2 patios! Spacious living room-cozy up to the fireplace on the main floor, 13 foot vaulted ceiling & sliders to private front patio. Formal dining room with wainscoting panels, overlooking the grand living room. Kitchen is both stylish & functional featuring stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and sliders to another patio. Head on upstairs to the primary bedroom with an ensuite offering walk-in closet, double sinks & shower. 2 additional large bedrooms & hall bathroom complete the 3rd floor. Rec Room or office in the English basement with a half bathroom, great for entertaining. Plus 2 car garage. This home is move in ready! Close to everything - parks, shopping, restaurants, Metra, major highways. Welcome to this dream home!
